Terrorsaur:





Terrorsaur couldn't stop growling at the mouse-bot. She was nothing but a 
servant to what he saw. What good was she? All that she did was give him 
energon that he didn't want. What a waste of bot!

He transformed to his robot mode and walked widely around her. He needed 
something to do, but he wasn't going to ask that female bot.

He looked around. Where was that other flier?
